	<h1>The Basics:</h1>
	<h4><br>

		<ul>
			<li> 
			Up&Away is a website developed to help progressive organizations find the funding they need to be successful.  
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			The website itself will be ran as a worker-owned cooperative.
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			All fundraising campaigns must be ran by a democratic workspace, non-profit, or sponsored by one of the above and fall within one or more of the following categories: 
			</li><br>
				<ol>

			<li> 
			Education
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Local Food
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Manual Labor, Domestic Services, & Manufacturing
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Community Programs + Grassroots Campaigns 
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Sustainability
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Web & Tech
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Media, Culture & Arts
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Business Services
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Cooperative Housing
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			Health Care & Self-Care
			</li><br>
		</ol>

			

		</ul>
</h4>
	<%= link_to "Next Page", '#2', class: "btn btn-medium btn-primary" %><br><br>
</div>


