	<h4><br>

		<ul>

			<li> 
			We will have active crowdfunding campaigns on our site, taking a percentage of each camapign's earnings (5%-10%). 
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			We will network with local artist and small businesess to provide high quality incentive offers for funders
			</li><br>

			<li> 
			We will work with local video artist to provide high quality video spots for each campaign.
			</li><br>
		</ul>
</h4>
